041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>让我们立即用我们这次创建的头像来尝试一下沙盒吧！入口处有一位导航员角色<strong>“密特拉”</strong> ，他将为玩家指引方向。门口还有其他玩家的头像，看起来已经很忙碌了。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>从入口处移动到模拟室。它的目的是模拟未探索地区的活动，似乎被定位为未来计划的全面沙箱的准备阶段。我的印象是空间一点也不宽敞。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>不过，我觉得没什么可做的，而且内容让我很惊讶，比我想象的更有成就感。这是因为<strong>构成沙盒的基础</strong>已经牢固建立，<strong>材料采集、加工、建造等</strong>要素逐渐解锁，可做的事情越来越多。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>本教程首先创建一个所谓的“豆腐屋”，它只是一个被墙壁包围的底座。玩过《我的世界》的用户将能够毫不犹豫地玩这款游戏，因为游戏涉及从附近的树木、石头和觅食中收集材料。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-jpg.webp 1000w, ht